# Pulsar API — manual HTTP requests
# Run with: JetBrains HTTP Client, VS Code REST Client, or httpx CLI
# Server: uv run uvicorn main:app --reload --port 8000

@base = http://localhost:8000

### Health check
GET {{base}}/api/health
Accept: application/json

### Chat — send a message (SSE stream)
POST {{base}}/api/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "What is retrieval-augmented generation?"
}

### Clear chat history
DELETE {{base}}/api/chat/history
Accept: application/json
